Package nl.uva.se.imppipes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Filter<I,O>
    A Filter is a Thread for processing elements in a pipe.
    FilterScaler<I,O>
    A FilterScaler has identical Filters process values.
    FinalFilter<O>
    A special type of Filter that collects the results it is told to process in a List so they can be obtained.
    FinalFilterScaler<O>
    This class is barely a wrapper for a FinalFilter so it can be chained after a list of FilterScalers.
    StartFilter<I>
    A special type of Filter that has all elements in a List processed by a chain of FilterScalers following this StartFilter.
